      "label": "What makes you the right hire for this position?",
      "type": "textarea",
      "required": true,
      "value": "I have been building and deploying complex AI and software systems in enterprise environments throughout my career at Microsoft, and I understand the fundamental challenge HappyRobot is solving: getting AI voice agents into real production workflows requires someone who can close the gap between what the model can do and what the customer's system actually needs. My experience managing technical integrations across sovereign cloud environments, running cross-functional deployments with enterprise customers, and debugging live system failures under pressure maps directly to the FDE role. Beyond the technical match, I think HappyRobot is solving one of the genuinely interesting deployment problems in AI right now - the phone call and voice layer is still mostly unautomated, and that's an asymmetric opportunity. I want to be on the team making that real.",
